channel.title: Client Jframe.class problem! Help! [$$$] I swear!
channel.description:
I'm tired of my client, I'm using Sagi-Evolution-X as a base source + client. I have getting started with source, changed home, added commands, new bosses and other stuff. The only problem i have is that my client has the old vote, donate, forums link buttons. (I guess you know what i mean.) Also, i can't change the title, or the links in Jframe.class, because if i compile after editing it says:
Client.java:2672: cannot access Jframe bad class file: .\Jframe.class class file has wrong version 8242.8224, should be 50.0 Please remove or make sure it appears in the correct subdirectory of the classpath.
new Jframe(args); ^ 1 Error Jatka painamalla mitä tahansa näppäintä
(Jatka painamalla... is finnish and means press any key to continue)
Please help here, or by teamviewer, i promise a juicy reward! Need help fast!
